name: Jumper「跳线」
author: Neo Ighodaro
description: 「直接从锁屏跳转到应用程序。」Jump into an application straight from the lockscreen. Jumper replaces the flashlight and camera lockscreen quick actions with custom applications. Supports iPhones running iOS 11.1.0 and up. You may need Little X or Shortcut Enabler IF you are not using the iPhone X or newer.
